  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink271-kilavi">talaimakaṉ varaivu vēṇṭiviṭat tamar maṟuttuḻic cevilikkut tōḻi yaṟattoṭu niṉṟatu.
          </p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> The confidante, standing in accordance with duty, to the foster-mother, when the relatives refused after the hero had asked for marriage.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink271">
<l>avarai yarunta manti pakarvar</l>
<l>pakkiṟ ṟōṉṟu nāṭaṉ vēṇṭiṟ</l>
<l>pacuppōl peṇṭirum peṟukuvaṉ</l>
<l>ṟolkē ḷākali ṉalkumā livaṭkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>If the man from the land </l>
        <l rend="indent">where the female monkey,</l>
        <l rend="indent">as it eats field beans,</l>
        <l rend="indent">appears like the bag of merchants (lit. announcement-makers),</l>
        <l>[so] desires, he can obtain women like cows.</l>
        <l>But since [his] friendship [with her] is ancient,</l>
        <l>he will give to her alone.</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
